{"tid":1957406,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[好撚柒]聶德權：世衛成員以主權國為單位　港台節目按約章處理","createTime":"2020-04-04T01:53:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T05:23:27.000Z","uid":51271,"like":33,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"f2b114a1118d4e9bc4fb7bae2c6f144f207c5162","tid":1957406,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T01:53:24.000Z","msg":"聶德權：世衛成員以主權國為單位 港台節目按約章處理<br />\n2020-04-04 HKT 09:49<br />\n<br />\n商務及經濟發展局局長邱騰華日前指出，港台節目訪問世界衛生組織官員的表達，有違一個中國原則及港台約章。政制及內地事務局局長聶德權出席一個電台節目後，被問到記者提問有何字眼違反一個中國原則，他說世衛成員是以主權國為單位，香港特區是以中國代表團成員的身分參與，有關世衛成員資格的問題非常清楚。<br />\n<br />\n聶德再被追問有關提問到底如何違反一個中國原則時說，相信有關的處理要按港台作為政府部門及公營廣播機構，按照相關機制及約章處理這個案。 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518819-20200404.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518819-20200404.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQys5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=e4bcdc6b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1518819-20200404.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=a0c95e01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1518819-20200404.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>好撚柒呀，你知唔知台灣之前用觀察員身份入Wuhan Hygiene Office呀</strong></span>"},{"pid":"4063bfd6b2c40ce718e0acc07529672327cb793d","tid":1957406,"uid":335434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T02:01:18.000Z","msg":"原來連佢都吼住廢人宗個位啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a482445d0d9a22ecc0d195c9049df29d941c01a7","tid":1957406,"uid":128923,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T02:09:20.000Z","msg":"歷屆參與世衛大會的成員分為三級，分別為「會員國」、「副會員（associate members）」及「觀察員」，會員國要求成員國是主權國家有投票權，但「副會員」及「觀察員」雖然有權參加會議，卻沒有投票權。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6cb105d3b7011c37c958dbdbad293ce10d9684e","tid":1957406,"uid":196924,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T02:14:58.000Z","msg":"咁點解香港澳門可以<span style=\"color: red;\">獨立</span>參加WHO西太平洋區域分部，台灣就唔可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解世衞網頁介紹陳馮富珍係<span style=\"color: red;\">香港</span>衞生署，而唔係中國廣東省香港市健衞委書記？<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Z0SjsN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Z0SjsN.jpg&h=ea5a53c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bded3f8551dc352a51a696865ae00ad9c84b211","tid":1957406,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T02:22:11.000Z","msg":"頂唔撚住喇<br />\n咪再問喇<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb53bb7fd801a3c2f69f49a1b0cd68fd114dc334","tid":1957406,"uid":188282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T02:31:52.000Z","msg":"香港特區是以<span style=\"color: red;\">中國代表團成員</span>的身分參與?<br />\n<br />\n文件真係咁寫?"},{"pid":"8b0fc77a6a790e742049559b20ec9215623548c9","tid":1957406,"uid":121197,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"fb53bb7fd801a3c2f69f49a1b0cd68fd114dc334","tid":1957406,"uid":188282,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T02:31:52.000Z","msg":"香港特區是以<span style=\"color: red;\">中國代表團成員</span>的身分參與?<br />\n<br />\n文件真係咁寫?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T02:34:59.000Z","msg":"一個中國點會有兩個會員<br />\n仲唔係搞港獨？"},{"pid":"337a205e254280409d8649bd4bc40fc6a31347ce","tid":1957406,"uid":48083,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T02:40:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3uAyOuF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3uAyOuF.png&h=4c91940a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http